{
  "global": "Navigate to the game releases section of the platform, apply an 'upcoming' release filter, sort by popularity, and surface the resulting ranked list.",
  "subtasks": [
    {
      "subtask": "Locate the game releases catalog or browse page",
      "atomics": [
        "Identify the navigation element or menu entry for 'Games' or 'Releases'",
        "Click the link/button to open the game catalog or releases page"
      ]
    },
    {
      "subtask": "Filter releases to show only upcoming games",
      "atomics": [
        "Locate the release-date or status filter control on the page",
        "Select or input the 'Upcoming' filter value",
        "Confirm/apply the filter and wait for the list to refresh"
      ]
    },
    {
      "subtask": "Sort the filtered list by popularity",
      "atomics": [
        "Locate the sort-by control or column header",
        "Select 'Most Popular' or 'Popularity' as the sort criterion",
        "Confirm descending order is applied and the list re-renders"
      ]
    },
    {
      "subtask": "Read and return the displayed list of most popular upcoming releases",
      "atomics": [
        "Scrape or read the game titles and associated metadata (release date, popularity score) from the rendered list",
        "Verify the list is non-empty and reflects the applied filters"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "global_atomics": [
    "Assert that both the 'upcoming' filter and the popularity sort are simultaneously active before recording results"
  ],
  "gold_actions": {
    "global": "Open the game releases catalog page, set release-status filter to 'Upcoming', set sort order to 'Most Popular' descending, and extract the resulting ordered game list.",
    "subtasks": [
      {
        "subtask": "Click the 'Games' or 'Releases' navigation link in the site header or sidebar",
        "atomics": [
          "Scan DOM for nav anchor with text matching /games|releases/i and click it",
          "Wait for the catalog page URL to resolve and main content to load"
        ]
      },
      {
        "subtask": "Apply 'Upcoming' release-date filter via the filter panel or dropdown",
        "atomics": [
          "Click the filter dropdown or checkbox group labeled 'Release Date' or 'Status'",
          "Select the option value 'upcoming' or equivalent enum token",
          "Click 'Apply' or observe automatic list reload triggered by filter change"
        ]
      },
      {
        "subtask": "Set sort criterion to popularity (descending) via the sort control",
        "atomics": [
          "Click the 'Sort by' dropdown and select 'Most Popular' or 'Popularity'",
          "Ensure sort direction is descending (highest popularity first)",
          "Wait for the page to re-render the reordered list"
        ]
      },
      {
        "subtask": "Extract the ordered list of upcoming game titles and their popularity indicators",
        "atomics": [
          "Query all game-card or list-row elements and collect title text and rank/score values",
          "Confirm list count > 0 and first item has the highest popularity value"
        ]
      }
    ],
    "global_atomics": [
      "Verify active filter badge or URL query params contain both 'upcoming' status and 'popularity' sort before finalizing the extracted list"
    ]
  }
}
```
